    "body" : "<p>Eclipse Toolbar > Windows > Preferences > General (Right side) > Editors (Right side) > Text Editors (Right side) > Annotations (Right side)</p>\n\n<p>For Occurrences and Write Occurrences, make sure you DO have the 'Text as highlighted' option checked for all of them. See screenshot below:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/Lw9zl.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/akK3J.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/viQ7H.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n"
  }, {
