      "comment_id" : 78703589,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I am using Eclipse Neon.3 and having this issue. This answer worked. What finally worked was to close all open files. I had a lot of open files."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
