      "body" : "This should be the accepted answer.  I was not aware of this short cut and tool bar action. And was very frustrated when the configured highlighting that I had for month in my editor suddenly disappeared (probably also when I wanted to organize the imports and accidently chose the wrong short cut combination as @flOw did"
