    "body" : "<p>This is what worked for me (credit to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/users/1178000/yardenst\">YardenST</a> from <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13237163/eclipse-syntax-highlighting-disappeared-for-one-of-my-files\">another thread</a>):\nInstead of double clicking file when opening, right click on file -> Open with -> Java editor </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/uZipD.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/uZipD.png\" alt=\"Screenshot\"></a></p>\n"
